@BFF.ProductCatalogService_HostAddress = https://localhost:7067

### Create a Category
POST {{BFF.ProductCatalogService_HostAddress}}/api/bff/v1/categories/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "name": "Books",
  "urlSlug": "books",
  "description": "All book categories"
}

### Create a Brand
POST {{BFF.ProductCatalogService_HostAddress}}/api/bff/v1/brands/
Content-Type: application/json

{
