### Create Dimensions
POST {{BFF.ProductCatalogService_HostAddress}}/api/bff/v1/dimensions/
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "id": "color",
    "displayType": "color",
    "name": "Color",
    "defaultValue": "nocolor",
    "values": [
      { "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001", "value": "red", "displayValue": "Red" },
      { "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002", "value": "blue", "displayValue": "Blue" }
    ]
  }
]

### Add Dimension Values
POST {{BFF.ProductCatalogService_HostAddress}}/api/bff/v1/dimensions/color/values
Content-Type: application/json

[
  { "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003", "value": "green" }
]

